descriptionHTML:
Enjoy your favorite music in a total new and wonderful dimension - with WonderMusic!

Key Features:
+ completely ads free
+ completely costs free usable (all In-App-Purchases are optional! donations!)
+ Theme Support
+ Material Design
+ individual customizable colors
+ Folder- & Playlist-Support
+ Headset-Support
+ Official support for Android Wear 2.0
+ Tablet-optimized
+ Support for device specific equalizer (if supported)

Of course you can join the Google+ Beta-Test under the following link:
https://plus.google.com/communities/102054446729756553390
